Cost-effectiveness analysis of dabigatran and anticoagulation monitoring 
strategies of vitamin K antagonist.

Carles M(1), Brosa M(2), Souto JC(3), Garcia-Alamino JM(4), Guyatt G(5), 
Alonso-Coello P(6)(7).

Author information:
(1)Departament d'Economia and CREIP, Universitat Rovira i Virgili, Avinguda de 
la Universitat 1, 43204, Reus, Spain. misericordia.carles@urv.net.
(2)Oblikue Consulting, Barcelona, SL, Spain. max.brosa@oblikue.com.
(3)Unitat d'Hemostàsia i Trombosi, Hospital de la Santa Creu i Sant Pau, 
Barcelona, España. jsouto@santpau.cat.
(4)Nuffield Department of Primary Care Health Sciences, University of Oxford, 
